ActFinancial Consumer Agency of Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of WERNER LIEDTKE of Ottawa, Ontario, to be interim Commissioner of the Financial Consumer Agency of Canada, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on December 31, 2024 or until such time as a new Commissioner is appointed, whichever occurs first.
